Personally identifiable information may include, but is not limited to your name
and email address
("Personal Information").
This Personal Information will be collected on a voluntary basis. If the User decides not to share this information, it might prevent them from experiencing the full potential of the App or Site..
While using our Site or App, we may collect certain non-personal identification information. This information cannot be used to identify or contact the User.
Non-personal information may include, but is not limited to your IP address, geographic region, device information, your use of our online and mobile products and services.
Log Data
Like many site operators, we collect information that your browser sends whenever you visit our Site
or App
("Log Data").
This Log Data may include information such as your computer's Internet Protocol ("IP") address, browser type, browser version, the pages of our Site that you visit, the time and date of your visit, the time spent on those pages and other statistics.
Cookies
Cookies are files with small amount of data, which may include an anonymous unique identifier. Cookies are sent to your browser from a web site and stored on your computer's hard drive.
Like many sites, we use "cookies" to collect information. You can instruct your browser to refuse all cookies or to indicate when a cookie is being sent. However, if you do not accept cookies, you may not be able to use some portions of our Site.
Analytics
Third party analytics companies (“Analytics Company”) may access anonymous information when you use our Site or App. Th
is anonymous information may include, but is not limited to User's IP address, Log Data, type of device, geographic region. The Analytics Company uses this data on our behalf to help us learn how our Site and App are used, to help us to improve the Site and App.
The Analytics Company collect and use the information under their own privacy policies, and your use of our Site or App is subject to those policies. The following list is a non-exclusive list of such Analytic Companies:
